Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.39,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Danger hides in shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:45.10,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}this wilderness of lost and found
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:50.94,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But in this closing darkness of enormous terror
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.95,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}there's a light we can see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.20,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Don't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:03.12,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}We still have a chance to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:09.54,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I feel us all rising up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.17,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Now, don't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:19.93,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even though the odds have left us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.31,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Feeling so small
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:28.48,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}but we can't stop now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.99,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I know there's a light
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:38.32,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Don't let it fade out, it's our heart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.20,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.20,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}We are not defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.46,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}We're not losing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:50.17,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}In these flames of war
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:55.97,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}We're rising up
