Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.39,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}陰影挾著危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:45.10,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}茫茫荒野 得失不斷上演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:50.94,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}但在可怖的黑暗中間 只要願意放眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.95,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}光明依然可見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.20,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}別放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:03.12,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一線希望就在眼前
